---
title: Seared Pork & Sesame Pumpkin Wedges with Teriyaki Glaze & Cucumber Salad
description: What’s an instant way to bring bold flavours to pork steaks? Add this sweet 'n' salty teriyaki glaze. Teamed with roasted pumpkin
wedges and a crisp salad, this meal will make your tastebuds sing!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
